# BRVMpy ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡®ğŸ“ˆ

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/brvmpy.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/brvmpy)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/brvmpy.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/brvmpy/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

**Scrape financial data from BRVM (Bourse RÃ©gionale des Valeurs MobiliÃ¨res) with ease!**

BRVMpy is a Python package that scrapes real-time financial data from the BRVM website and returns clean Pandas DataFrames ready for analysis.

---

## ğŸŒ About BRVM

The **BRVM (Bourse RÃ©gionale des Valeurs MobiliÃ¨res)** is the regional stock exchange serving 8 West African countries:
- ğŸ‡§ğŸ‡¯ Benin
- ğŸ‡§ğŸ‡« Burkina Faso
- ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡® CÃ´te d'Ivoire
- ğŸ‡¬ğŸ‡¼ Guinea-Bissau
- ğŸ‡²ğŸ‡± Mali
- ğŸ‡³ğŸ‡ª Niger
- ğŸ‡¸ğŸ‡³ Senegal
- ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¬ Togo

Website: https://www.brvm.org

---

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ“Š **Actions (Stocks)**: Get real-time stock prices, volumes, and changes
- ğŸ’° **Obligations (Bonds)**: Scrape bond market data
- ğŸ“ˆ **Indices**: Fetch market indices (BRVM 10, BRVM Composite, etc.)
- ğŸ“‰ **Volumes**: Get trading volume data
- ğŸ¼ **Pandas Ready**: All data returned as clean DataFrames
- ğŸš€ **Easy to Use**: Simple, intuitive API
- ğŸ”„ **Auto-Updated**: Always scrapes the latest data from BRVM website
- ğŸ¤– **Selenium Powered**: Reliable web scraping with headless Chrome

---

